line_up: Indira Paganotto, Siles, Lucas Cabello, Sou Allen, Domen, Tony Fimia
venue_information: S — 21 — Diciembre. Barraca presenta a Indira Paganotto Indira Paganotto born in 1992 and is currently one of the most talented producer of the national electronic music. Indira has had an eclectical musical education . Her father, DJ in Goa (India) in the 90 was her musical reference from small and his collection of goa trance was the perfect library for the young italocanary. At 16 she became interested in the vinyls of her father and began to DJing in clubs on the island. The following year Ian Pooley signed her in his label , she created her first vinyl "Underground Love " with collaborations Jef K Gwen Maze, G-Room and Ian Pooley. She released her second vinyl in 2014 in Pooledmusic, called "Time out Man " Having played in some of the best clubs and Festivals like Lollapalooza Festival (Argentina) , Daydream Festival , Rex Club (Paris), Egg Club (London), Harry Klein (Munich), Gare Porto (Portugal),Goa - Fabrik (Madrid); and sharing the stage with International artist like , Oxia, Philip Bader, Ian Pooley, Sven Vath, Marc Houle, Dasha Rush, Steve Bug, among others. Indira sets are full of groove and forcefulness, she draws on elements from all genres including psyprogressive, minimal, techno, not afraid to blend genres or styles , always with organic acid touches ,reminiscent of her heritage musical. This energetic eclecticism has become her main signature, with her constant smile. 2020 comes loaded with new features for Indira Paganotto, she is preparing her first album and a new label that soon we will had news .
event_location_details: With more than 50 years of history behind it, Barraca has been open since the summer of 1965. In the mid-80s its popularity rose due to the great electronic music movement that took place in Spain. The movement is known as "La Ruta del Bacalao", where they offered a host of festivals and festivals along the Spanish Mediterranean coast, especially the Valencian one. Barraca took advantage of the movement and positioned itself as one of the greatest exponents of this underground movement. Baracca is divided up into 4 rooms: - Circo: is the largest room, with a capacity for almost a thousand people, the place where the great events of Valencia are held. DJs ranking amongst Richie Hawtin, Laurent Garnier, Ricardo Villalobos and Danny Tenaglia have passed through the booth. No doubt, the best. - La Barraca: the original club underwent an impressive renovation in 2007 that has allowed it to continue offering the best electronic music in Valencia. - Showroom: this is your alternative room, where the young and rising names of techno and house host more experimental sessions. Dedicated to house music since its beginnings, its original name was simply, House Room. - Terraza: with a capacity of 600 people, it’s a venue to rival some of the best in Ibiza. During the summer, it’s always the first to open. It has a huge fan base and the coolest sounds of Valencia. Barraca has established itself as one of the most important underground clubs in Spain and hosts a lot of great sets by the most anticipated artists. With exactly 12,738 sessions and more than 21,400 DJs that have passed through the Valencian club, we can say that Barraca is not just a lot of good electronic music. Barraca is synonymous with quality. Barraca delivers the best techno and the best house in all its aspects. DJs and producers like Ricardo Villalobos, Loco Dice, Tania Vulcano, Marco Carola, Ellen Allien and Óscar Mulero are a clear example of this. The dress code is casual, informal, underground. With Xceed you can buy your early bird ticket for Barraca. Alternatively, you can buy it at the door on the night. Barraca is open at the weekends and the night before some holidays. Barraca opens its doors at 00:00 until 06:00 in the morning. The average price of entry is between 15€ and 25€.

event_location_details: Latex Club in Valencia is presented as a dynamic and versatile space, which from now on opens its doors with a varied offer for each day of the week: Thursdays with Moova: a Black Music label that combines black music, fashion and parties inspired by cities like Paris, London and Berlin, offering an international and avant-garde experience in Valencia. Fridays with Grasa: a new approach to techno “without a monocle” to give space and visibility to younger and less normative groups. On Saturdays will surprise you with a different party every week, with electronic rhythms, tech groove and punk funk for an unforgettable night. Latex Club is thus positioned as an essential place in Valencia's nightlife, combining different styles and atmospheres to satisfy all music lovers.

venue_information: Kidrizzo + La3 djs
event_location_details: It’s been open for less than 10 years but La3 has quickly become one of the most iconic clubs in Valencia. This club boasts quality sound systems, which have recently been upgraded to the Funktion-One system. The club’s name comes from the 3 rooms within the club: Main Room, Oven Club y Sala2, which have hosted the most famous national and international artists such as Jeff Mills, Nina Kraviz, Laurent Garnier, Seth Troxler, 2manydjs, Vitalic and Flux Pavilion among many others. La3 is not only one of the best party clubs in Valencia but it is a meeting point for true music lovers. In terms of music, La3 is now adding more urban styles such as trap, R&B and hip-hop and the popular Friday night is adapting to the needs of its public, the young and cosmopolitan masses. To satisfy you on Saturday nights, there is a new event at the club called “Electric Saturdays”, where you can enjoy the best national and international techno and house DJs in any of the 3 rooms that the venue boasts. If La3 is known for something in particular, it’s because of its high quality music played weekend after weekend.

event_genres: Elegant, Cozy, House, Groove Techno, Minimal
venue_information: La Cuina is much more than an electronic music party. It is the natural evolution of the Music To Take Away brand, bringing house, groove and minimal to the most exclusive and captivating locations. At La Cuina, we have found our home, a fixed space that symbolizes the essence of a delivery, the dark kitchen: a place where the purest and most authentic musical experience is cooked, ready to be enjoyed by lovers of electronic music in its own form. Here, music is the main course and each event, a feast for the senses. In the fiery heart of Ruzafa, where the nights boil and creativity has no limits, La Cuina hides. This clandestine kitchen is for those who know what a real party is: pure slow-cooked electronic music. Get ready to savor the most exquisite house, from the groove that catches you to the minimal that envelops you. Each party is a custom-made tasting menu, where the beats are the main course and the dance floor is the table where it is served. Photos? No. Videos? Forget it. VIP or guest lists? Here the desire rules, not the name. Here you don't come to posturing, you come to enjoy the authentic recipe: party without filters, music without concessions, rhythm direct to the palate. What happens at La Cuina stays within its four walls: well-kept secrets, like grandma's recipe. Are you hungry? I hope, because at La Cuina, we don't leave anyone hungry.

event_location_details: En 1984 sobre las cenizas de la discoteca San Francisco voló por primera vez el murciélago más emblemático de la noche. Abría Spook Factory, el templo de la música Valenciana. Un espacio para la experimentación sensorial que marcó un antes y un después en la historia del clubbing. Hoy Spook sigue siendo historia viva de Valencia, ofreciendo una programación musical de vanguardia nacional e internacional. Todos los sábados desde las 18:00h a las 7:30h tienes una cita con la música, la catarsis y la vanguardia. Bandas, Lives, Dj’s, Foodtrucks y mucho más. #TodosLosSabadosUnFestival.

venue_information: Wateke especial año nuevo
event_location_details: It’s been open for less than 10 years but La3 has quickly become one of the most iconic clubs in Valencia. This club boasts quality sound systems, which have recently been upgraded to the Funktion-One system. The club’s name comes from the 3 rooms within the club: Main Room, Oven Club y Sala2, which have hosted the most famous national and international artists such as Jeff Mills, Nina Kraviz, Laurent Garnier, Seth Troxler, 2manydjs, Vitalic and Flux Pavilion among many others. La3 is not only one of the best party clubs in Valencia but it is a meeting point for true music lovers. In terms of music, La3 is now adding more urban styles such as trap, R&B and hip-hop and the popular Friday night is adapting to the needs of its public, the young and cosmopolitan masses. To satisfy you on Saturday nights, there is a new event at the club called “Electric Saturdays”, where you can enjoy the best national and international techno and house DJs in any of the 3 rooms that the venue boasts. If La3 is known for something in particular, it’s because of its high quality music played weekend after weekend.

venue_information: It’s been open for less than 10 years but La3 has quickly become one of the most iconic clubs in Valencia. This club boasts quality sound systems, which have recently been upgraded to the Funktion-One system. The club’s name comes from the 3 rooms within the club: Main Room, Oven Club y Sala2, which have hosted the most famous national and international artists such as Jeff Mills, Nina Kraviz, Laurent Garnier, Seth Troxler, 2manydjs, Vitalic and Flux Pavilion among many others. La3 is not only one of the best party clubs in Valencia but it is a meeting point for true music lovers. In terms of music, La3 is now adding more urban styles such as trap, R&B and hip-hop and the popular Friday night is adapting to the needs of its public, the young and cosmopolitan masses. To satisfy you on Saturday nights, there is a new event at the club called “Electric Saturdays”, where you can enjoy the best national and international techno and house DJs in any of the 3 rooms that the venue boasts. If La3 is known for something in particular, it’s because of its high quality music played weekend after weekend.

event_location_details: Jagger Pub is not just your typical pub, it is a venue with character and style that offers a club-like experience. Located in the heart of the city, it's the perfect place to enjoy timeless hits and a vibrant atmosphere. With its sleek and modern decor, Jagger Pub provides the perfect backdrop for a night out with friends. The expertly crafted cocktail menu and wide selection of drinks make it the ideal spot for those looking to start their night off with a bang. As the night progresses, the venue transforms into a full-on club, with top-notch DJs spinning the latest and greatest tracks to keep you moving all night long. Whether you're in the mood for dancing or just hanging out with friends, Jagger Pub is the place to be. Come and experience the electric atmosphere and unforgettable nights at Jagger Pub.
